                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/79930612/">星星雨☆</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">圣奥斯定的忏悔录是圣经最好的神学注释，圣阿奎那的神学大全是圣经最好的哲学注释。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
        <p>&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3552733/comments/">更多短评 8 条</a></p>
